summary: Cartoon Network, or CN, is an American TV channel owned by Warner Bros. Discovery. It started in 1992 and is based in Atlanta, Georgia. The channel shows animated shows for kids, from action to comedy. It's open daily from 6 a.m. to 5 p.m. ET/PT. Cartoon Network targets kids aged 6 to 12, with special blocks like Cartoonito for preschoolers and Adult Swim for young adults. As of 2023, it reaches about 66 million U.S. homes.
title: Cartoon Network
